<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 图片不存在</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: "Microsoft Yahei", system-ui, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* 大号404数字 */
        .error-num {
            font-size: 120px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #5c7cfa;
            letter-spacing: 12px;
            text-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(92, 124, 250, 0.35);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
            user-select: none;
        }

        /* 文字说明容器 */
        .error-text {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #495057;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 2.2;
        }

        /* 链接统一样式 */
        .link-btn {
            color: #5c7cfa;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 2px 4px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .link-btn:hover {
            background-color: #5c7cfa;
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* 悬浮动画 */
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
        }

        /* 移动端适配 */
        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .error-num {
                font-size: 80px;
                letter-spacing: 6px;
            }
            .error-text {
                font-size: 16px;
                line-height: 2;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-num">404</div>
    <div class="error-text">
        您的图片已到期或违规已被删除<br>
        可<a href="https://picui.cn/user/tickets" target="_blank" class="link-btn">提交工单</a>
        或<a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#741d19131b07340e1c010e1c01075a171a" class="link-btn">邮件咨询</a><br>
        图床地址：<a href="https://picui.cn" target="_blank" class="link-btn">picui.cn</a>
    </div>
<script data-cfasync="false" src="/cdn-cgi/scripts/5c5dd728/cloudflare-static/email-decode.min.js"></script></body>
</html>
